=You will receive a content title and an angle. Return 5‚Äì8 non-overlapping questions in JSON array format that cover everything needed to write excellent content as it breaks down the topic into sub-questions.

Guidelines:  
- Start with simple, short broad questions for example to define the terms (e.g., What is X?, Why is X important?, How to do X?).  
- Then move into more specific, advanced, or analytical questions.  
- Ensure questions together form a complete coverage of the topic.   

